===Hardware specification=== *CPU: ''[[Marvell]]'' 88F6281 @ 1.2GHz *Memory: 512MB Samsung DDR2 SDRAM *Storage: 512MB Samsung NAND Flash *Network 1x Gigabit Ethernet *USB: 1x USB 2.0 *Power Source: AC 100-240V, 50-60Hz
